	(pam_poldi_options_cb): Handle ARG_WAIT_TIMEOUT.
	(wait_for_card): New variables; TIMEOUT, WAIT; initialize them
	depending on FAKE and PAM_POLDI_OPT.TIMEOUT; pass TIMEOUT and WAIT
	to card_init.
